              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/23067003-lily?shelf=insta-love-or-lust-baby">insta-love-or-lust-baby</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/23067003-lily?shelf=reclusive-loner-protag">reclusive-loner-protag</a>, 
